import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../Navbar/Navbar'
import {
  MainContainer,
  MainContent,
  MainItems,
  MainH1,
  MainH2,
  MainBtn
} from './MainElements'


const Main = () => {
  return (
    <MainContainer>
      <Navbar />
      <MainContent>
        <MainItems>
          <MainH1>Cheefa's Fried Pies</MainH1>
          <MainH2>Have a Taste of the Glory</MainH2>
          <MainBtn>Order here</MainBtn>
        </MainItems>
      </MainContent>
    </MainContainer>
  )
}

export default Main
